name: My Life with the Walter Boys
original_name: My Life with the Walter Boys
overview: When a tragedy disrupts her life, a teen moves in with her guardian's big family in a small town and learns new lessons about love, hope and friendship.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: When a tragedy disrupts her life, a teen moves in with her guardian's big family in a small town and learns new lessons about love, hope and friendship.

episodes.name: Welcome to Colorado
episodes.overview: After a tragic loss, Jackie moves in with the Walters and tries to adjust to small-town life. But a new home and new high school bring new challenges.

episodes.name: Live a Little
episodes.overview: When the brothers make a bet involving a prank on Jackie, she turns to Katherine but learns that the boys have their own way of handling their issues.

episodes.name: The Cole Effect
episodes.overview: At the Homecoming Huddle, Alex and Jackie run the Walter family cider cart together with help from Cole, who struggles to accept life without football.

episodes.name: Nineteen
episodes.overview: On Lucy's birthday, Jackie decides to skip school and attend a lake house party with Cole, where the two play a high-stakes version of Truth or Dare.

episodes.name: Thanksgiving
episodes.overview: Jackie wants to avoid the first Thanksgiving without her family, but a surprise visitor lifts her mood and presents her with a difficult choice.

episodes.name: Baggage
episodes.overview: Before the big bonfire, Jackie learns about Cole and Alex's history with another girl. At the party, relationships new and old go up in flames.

episodes.name: Small Town Rumors
episodes.overview: As rumors fly about the Walter boys, Alex and Cole's sibling rivalry reaches its breaking point. Later, the family deals with an unsettling emergency.

episodes.name: Spinning Out
episodes.overview: When Katherine wins an award for her veterinarian work, the family jumps to support her  except Cole, who instead heads down a path of self-destruction.

episodes.name: Revolutions
episodes.overview: Jackie misses Alex's county fair rodeo for an important interview and tries to keep her distance from Cole after their hurtful exchange.

episodes.name: Happily Ever After
episodes.overview: With the Walter boys' help, Jackie diligently plans a picture-perfect ranch wedding. But no amount of checklists can prepare her for what happens next.
